A4.text: Del Monte Foods Inc. is an American food production and distribution company and subsidiary of NutriAsia, headquartered in Walnut Creek, California.

A5.text: In the 1880s, an Oakland, California, foods distributor used the Del Monte name to market a premium blend of coffee that had been prepared for the hotel.
